# ELEVON ERP — Project Architecture

## Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Frontend | Angular | 21.2.7 |
| TypeScript | TypeScript | 5.9.3 |
| UI Kit | Angular Material + ng-bootstrap | 21.2.5 / 20.0.0 |
| Charts | ApexCharts | 5.3.5 |
| CSS | Bootstrap 4.6.2 + Custom SCSS tokens | — |
| Backend | Spring Boot (Java/Maven) | `erp-system-backend/` |
| i18n | ngx-translate | ar.json + en.json |
| Export | xlsx-js-style | 1.2.0 |
| Animation | GSAP | 3.14.2 |
| Node | Node.js | 20+ required |

## Project root layout

```
erp Project/
├── erp-system-frontend/      ← Angular app (work here)
├── erp-system-backend/       ← Spring Boot backend
├── ops/
│   ├── frontend-run/         ← proxy.conf.json, run-frontend.ps1
│   └── docker/               ← build-and-push scripts
├── scripts/                  ← deployment utils
├── infra/                    ← infrastructure config
└── .runtime/                 ← launcher-state.json (runtime backend URL)
```

## How to run

### Frontend
```powershell
# From project root:
.\run-frontend.ps1      # or run-frontend.bat
# Auto-detects port 4200–4210 | Reads backend URL from .runtime/launcher-state.json
```

### Backend
- Located at `erp-system-backend/` (Spring Boot / Maven)
- Backend port: **8081**
- API base: `http://127.0.0.1:8081/api/v1`

### Dev proxy
`ops/frontend-run/proxy.conf.json` proxies `/api/v1` → `http://127.0.0.1:8081`

## API base URL

```typescript
// environment.ts / environment.prod.ts
apiUrl = window.__ERP_API_URL__ ?? '/api/v1'
```

## Frontend folder structure

```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── core/
│   │   ├── auth/           ← AuthService, AuthGuard, AdminGuard, PermissionGuard
│   │   ├── constants/      ← app constants
│   │   ├── i18n/           ← translate setup
│   │   ├── interceptors/   ← HTTP interceptors (auth token)
│   │   ├── models/         ← TypeScript interfaces
│   │   ├── services/       ← ThemeService, PermissionService, etc.
│   │   └── utils/
│   ├── modules/            ← 27 lazy-loaded feature modules (see below)
│   ├── shared/
│   │   ├── components/     ← 27 reusable components (see below)
│   │   └── directives/
│   └── theme/
│       └── layout/admin/
│           ├── nav-bar/    ← Topbar (nav-bar.component, nav-right/)
│           └── navigation/ ← Sidebar (navigation.component)
├── assets/
│   ├── i18n/               ← ar.json, en.json
│   ├── images/brand/       ← ELEVON logo SVGs (coreerp-*.svg kept as filenames)
│   └── fonts/
└── scss/
    ├── erp-estate-tokens.scss     ← ALL design tokens (use this as source of truth)
    ├── erp-estate-shell.scss      ← sidebar + topbar shell layout
    ├── erp-estate-utilities.scss  ← utility classes + animations
    ├── page-ui.scss               ← shared page/card/table/pagination styles
    └── design-system/tokens.scss  ← legacy token bridge
```

