## Auth guards

| Guard | File | Behavior |
|-------|------|----------|
| `AuthGuard` | `core/auth/auth.guard.ts` | Requires valid token → else `/auth/signin` |
| `AdminGuard` | `core/auth/admin.guard.ts` | Requires role `ADMIN` → else `/dashboard` |
| `PermissionGuard` | `core/auth/permission.guard.ts` | Checks `menuItemId` + `permissionAction` in route data |

## User roles

| Role | Access |
|------|--------|
| `ADMIN` | All modules including `/accountants` |
| `ACCOUNTANT` | All modules except `/accountants` |

## localStorage keys

| Key | Value |
|-----|-------|
| `erp_auth_token` | JWT access token |
| `erp_auth_refresh_token` | Refresh token |
| `erp_theme_mode` | `'dark'` \| `'light'` (default: `'dark'`) |
| `erp_ui_menu_cache_v2` | Sidebar menu cache |

## Critical rules — do not break

- **Never touch backend** unless frontend compilation requires a small interface fix
- **Never break routing** — all 27 routes must remain navigable
- **Never remove features** — only add or improve
- **Login screen** — layout is locked; only visual (colors, shadow, glassmorphism) changes allowed
- **API calls** — always go through services in `core/services/` or module services; never call `HttpClient` directly from components
- **i18n** — all user-facing strings must use `translate` pipe or `TranslateService`; never hardcode Arabic/English text
